%h1.sm What are you calculating?
- if @categories.any?
    %p Tell Phylator what area of science your calculation belongs to.
    .flex.center
        .myg-list
            - @categories.each do |category|
                .myg-list--item= link_to category, how_url(quantity: params[:quantity], unit: params[:unit], category: category)
        %p.sm or
        = link_to 'Make a custom calculation', how_url(quantity: params[:quantity], unit: params[:unit])
- else
    %p Phylator couldn't find any predefined calculations.
    = link_to 'Continue', measurements_url(quantity: params[:quantity], unit: params[:unit])
